        <div2>
          <figure n="DrawTheLine.17.1.bqscan" rend="file" width="250" height="313">
          	<figTranscr>DRAW the LINE AT SAMBO’S!<lb/>
          	<lb/>
          	16 out of 19 workers are scheduled by management to be fired<lb/>
          	on trumped-up charges. New management wants “new blood”;<lb/>
          	workers who have worked there for years are being fired BECAUSE<lb/>
          	they have worked there for years. The frivolity of the managers<lb/>
          	and owners must cease. No one is safe. So Sambo’s workers<lb/>
          	have chosen to resist — not only for themselves, but for<lb/>
          	all of us who work for a living or seek work.<lb/>
          	<lb/>
          	JOIN THE WORKERS AT THEIR WORKPLACE<lb/>
          	5th and Harrison<lb/>
          	8:00 pm Thursday November 11th<lb/>
          	<lb/>
          	The line is drawn.</figTranscr>
          </figure>
        </div2>
